<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= serviceName %> - 服務文檔</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50 0%, #45a049 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header .service-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .version-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 5px solid #4CAF50;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .feature-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2E7D32;
        }

        .feature-description {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .endpoint-list {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .endpoint-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-left: 3px solid #4CAF50;
        }

        .architecture-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .architecture-title {
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .architecture-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .architecture-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #c8e6c9;
        }

        .architecture-item h4 {
            color: #2E7D32;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .examples-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .example-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }

        .example-title {
            color: #2E7D32;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .step-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .step-item {
            background: white;
            margin: 5px 0;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 3px solid #FF9800;
        }

        .navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .navigation {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="service-icon">⚙️</div>
            <h1><%= serviceName %></h1>
            <div class="description"><%= description %></div>
            <div class="version-badge">版本 <%= version %></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Core Features -->
        <div class="features-grid">
            <!-- User Preferences -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">👤</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">使用者偏好設定</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    管理使用者的個人化設定和偏好，包括介面配置、通知設定和系統選項
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /user-preferences - 獲取使用者設定</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /user-preferences - 創建使用者設定</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">PUT /user-preferences/:id - 更新設定</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">DELETE /user-preferences/:id - 刪除設定</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- System Configuration -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🔧</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">系統設定管理</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    提供系統層級的配置管理，包括功能開關、參數調整和環境配置
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /system/config - 獲取系統配置</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">PUT /system/config - 更新系統配置</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /system/features - 功能開關列表</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /system/features/toggle - 切換功能</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Data Processing -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">📊</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">資料處理工具</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    通用的資料處理功能，包括格式轉換、驗證、清理和統計分析
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /data/validate - 資料驗證</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /data/transform - 格式轉換</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /data/analyze - 統計分析</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /data/export - 資料匯出</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Utility Functions -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🛠️</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">工具函數庫</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    提供系統所需的通用工具函數，包括檔案處理、日期時間和字串操作
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /utils/file/upload - 檔案上傳</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /utils/time/format - 時間格式化</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /utils/string/hash - 字串雜湊</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /utils/system/info - 系統資訊</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Architecture -->
        <div class="architecture-section">
            <h2 class="architecture-title">🏗️ 服務架構</h2>
            <div class="architecture-grid">
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>🗄️ 資料庫</h4>
                    <p>MySQL + MongoDB</p>
                    <small>設定資料與檔案存儲</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>⚡ 快取</h4>
                    <p>Redis</p>
                    <small>設定快取與會話</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>🔗 通訊</h4>
                    <p>gRPC + HTTP</p>
                    <small>跨服務通訊協定</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>📡 訊息佇列</h4>
                    <p>RabbitMQ</p>
                    <small>異步任務處理</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>🔍 服務發現</h4>
                    <p>Consul</p>
                    <small>服務註冊與發現</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>📋 架構模式</h4>
                    <p>CQRS</p>
                    <small>命令查詢責任分離</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Usage Examples -->
        <div class="examples-section">
            <h2 class="architecture-title">💡 使用範例</h2>
            
            <div class="example-card">
                <div class="example-title">👤 使用者偏好設定流程</div>
                <ol class="step-list">
                    <li class="step-item">獲取使用者當前設定：GET /user-preferences</li>
                    <li class="step-item">驗證設定資料格式：POST /data/validate</li>
                    <li class="step-item">更新使用者偏好：PUT /user-preferences/:id</li>
                    <li class="step-item">確認設定生效：GET /user-preferences/:id</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="example-card">
                <div class="example-title">⚙️ 系統配置管理流程</div>
                <ol class="step-list">
                    <li class="step-item">檢查系統狀態：GET /system/config</li>
                    <li class="step-item">查看功能開關：GET /system/features</li>
                    <li class="step-item">切換功能狀態：POST /system/features/toggle</li>
                    <li class="step-item">更新系統配置：PUT /system/config</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Navigation -->
        <div class="navigation">
            <a href="/api/docs/general/typedoc" class="nav-btn">
                🔧 查看技術文檔 (TypeDoc)
            </a>
            <a href="/api/docs" class="nav-btn">
                🏠 返回文檔中心
            </a>
            <a href="/api/health" class="nav-btn">
                ❤️ 服務健康檢查
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>🕒 最後更新：<%= new Date(lastUpdated).toLocaleString('zh-TW') %></p>
            <p>🏗️ AIOT Development Team | 通用功能與系統管理微服務</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>